Preston Foster https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preston_Foster 0 Preston Stratton Foster (August 24, 1900 – July 14, 1970), was an American actor of stage, film, radio, and television, whose career spanned nearly four decades. He also had a career as a vocalist.
